comments: Bazemore (ATL) places two hands on Booker's (PHX) body and affects his ability to get to the pass.
Collins (ATL) does not turn into Booker's (PHX) path during the dribble-hand off.
RLB shows Ayton (PHX) extends his arm into Prince's (ATL) body and affects his driving shot attempt.
LAR shows Ayton (PHX) maintains his pivot foot after his gather.
LLS and RLS show Prince (ATL) does not make contact to Ayton's (PHX) arm and does not affect his ability to pass.
Oubre Jr. (PHX) makes marginal contact with Young (ATL) after he has released his shot attempt.
LLS shows Bridges (PHX) makes contact to Young's (ATL) arm, and the contact occurs after Young's gather.
Johnson (PHX) makes incidental contact with Collins (ATL) after Collins has secured the ball on the perimeter.
Ayton (PHX) legally contests Dedmon's (ATL) shot at the rim.
LAR shows Young (ATL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Johnson's (PHX) shot attempt.
RAR shows Dedmon (ATL) does not make contact to Johnson's (PHX) arm as he defends the shot attempt.
RLB shows Bridges (PHX) places two hands on Young (ATL) during his drive and affects his SQBR.
Prince (ATL) engages with Johnson (PHX) but does not affect his FOM during the inbound.
LAR shows Bazemore (ATL) legally contests Booker's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Bridges (PHX) and Collins (ATL) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
RLB shows Oubre Jr. (PHX) makes contact to Collins' (ATL) arm that affects his ability to control the ball.
LAR shows Bazemore (ATL) makes body to body contact with Booker (PHX) that affects his jump shot attempt.
Oubre Jr. (PHX) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
